              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41010905/" class="">第324页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/150554944/" class=" " title="朝闻道">朝闻道</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="41010905">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">历史只能从细节处发现真相。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-12-30 16:23</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
